# Homepage Components

The main landing page ([src/pages/HomePage.vue](mdc:src/pages/HomePage.vue)) is composed of several section components:

## Header and Navigation
- [src/components/Header.vue](mdc:src/components/Header.vue) - The main navigation header

## Content Sections
- [src/components/HeroSection.vue](mdc:src/components/HeroSection.vue) - Hero section at the top of the page
- [src/components/FeaturesSection.vue](mdc:src/components/FeaturesSection.vue) - Features showcase
- [src/components/AdvantagesSection.vue](mdc:src/components/AdvantagesSection.vue) - Advantages of the app/product
- [src/components/AboutUsSection.vue](mdc:src/components/AboutUsSection.vue) - About the company/team
- [src/components/DownloadSection.vue](mdc:src/components/DownloadSection.vue) - App download information

## Footer
- [src/components/FooterSection.vue](mdc:src/components/FooterSection.vue) - Page footer with links and information

These components are designed to be reused across different pages of the site when needed.
